    "title": "Angola : Roads (OpenStreetMap Export)",
    "name": "hotosm_ago_roads",
    "notes": "Road network across the region from OSM. Includes everything tagged with <code>highway</code>: motorways, residential streets, service roads, footways, and trails. Useful for routing, accessibility analysis, and evacuation planning.  OpenStreetMap is a free, collaborative world map built by volunteers. Completeness varies by region: urban areas are usually well-mapped, remote areas may be incomplete. Cross-check critical decisions with local field knowledge. <ul> <li>Source: <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org\">OpenStreetMap</a></li> <li>OSM tags: <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:highway\">Key:highway</a></li> <li>Part of many  <a href=\"https://data.humdata.org/organization/hot\">exports grid on HDX</a> by the <a href=\"https://www.hotosm.org/en/\">HOT</a></li> </ul>",
